  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Supporting Directorate General for Migration Management (DGMM) Efforts in Enhancing the Capacity of Removal Centres within the Framework of International Human Rights Standards Phase-II</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The second phase of this project seeks to mainstream a human rights-based approach in Provincial Directorates of Migration Management (PDMMs) responsible for running removal centres (RCs) through the provision of comprehensive training and guidance on human rights of migrants. In addition, IOM will seek to contribute to the efforts of the Diretorate General for Migration Management (DGMM) in strengthening the institutional capacity, staff well-being and material conditions in RCs.</narrative>
  </description>
